{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Chris Anderson: Welcome to TED."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"Richard Branson: Thank you very much. The first TED has been great."}]},{"cues":[{"time":5000,"text":"CA: Have you met anyone interesting?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":7000,"text":"RB: Well, the nice thing about TED is everybody's interesting."},{"time":10000,"text":"I was very glad to see Goldie Hawn,"},{"time":12000,"text":"because I had an apology to make to her."},{"time":15000,"text":"I'd had dinner with her about two years ago and I'd --"},{"time":20000,"text":"she had this big wedding ring and I put it on my finger and I couldn't get it off."},{"time":25000,"text":"And I went home to my wife that night"},{"time":28000,"text":"and she wanted to know why I had another woman's big,"},{"time":30000,"text":"massive, big wedding ring on my finger."},{"time":33000,"text":"And, anyway, the next morning we had to go along to the jeweler"},{"time":35000,"text":"and get it cut off."},{"time":37000,"text":"So -- (Laughter) --"},{"time":41000,"text":"so apologies to Goldie."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42000,"text":"CA: That's pretty good."},{"time":44000,"text":"So, we're going to put up some slides"},{"time":47000,"text":"of some of your companies here."},{"time":49000,"text":"You've started one or two in your time."},{"time":52000,"text":"So, you know, Virgin Atlantic, Virgin Records --"},{"time":55000,"text":"I guess it all started with a magazine called Student."},{"time":58000,"text":"And then, yes, all these other ones as well. I mean, how do you do this?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":64000,"text":"RB: I read all these sort of TED instructions:"},{"time":67000,"text":"you must not talk about your own business, and this,"},{"time":69000,"text":"and now you ask me."},{"time":70000,"text":"So I suppose you're not going to be able to kick me off the stage,"},{"time":72000,"text":"since you asked the question."},{"time":74000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":75000,"text":"CA: It depends what the answer is though."}]},{"cues":[{"time":78000,"text":"RB: No, I mean, I think I learned early on that if you can run one company,"},{"time":84000,"text":"you can really run any companies."},{"time":85000,"text":"I mean, companies are all about finding the right people,"},{"time":89000,"text":"inspiring those people, you know, drawing out the best in people."},{"time":95000,"text":"And I just love learning and I'm incredibly inquisitive"},{"time":100000,"text":"and I love taking on, you know, the status quo"},{"time":104000,"text":"and trying to turn it upside down."},{"time":106000,"text":"So I've seen life as one long learning process."},{"time":110000,"text":"And if I see -- you know, if I fly on somebody else's airline"},{"time":114000,"text":"and find the experience is not a pleasant one, which it wasn't,"},{"time":118000,"text":"21 years ago, then I'd think, well, you know, maybe I can create"},{"time":122000,"text":"the kind of airline that I'd like to fly on."},{"time":125000,"text":"And so, you know, so got one secondhand 747 from Boeing and gave it a go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":131000,"text":"CA: Well, that was a bizarre thing,"},{"time":132000,"text":"because you made this move that a lot of people advised you was crazy."},{"time":137000,"text":"And in fact, in a way, it almost took down your empire at one point."},{"time":142000,"text":"I had a conversation with one of the investment bankers who,"},{"time":145000,"text":"at the time when you basically sold Virgin Records"},{"time":149000,"text":"and invested heavily in Virgin Atlantic,"},{"time":151000,"text":"and his view was that you were trading, you know,"},{"time":154000,"text":"the world's fourth biggest record company"},{"time":156000,"text":"for the twenty-fifth biggest airline and that you were out of your mind."},{"time":160000,"text":"Why did you do that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":162000,"text":"RB: Well, I think that there's a very thin dividing line between success and failure."},{"time":168000,"text":"And I think if you start a business without financial backing,"},{"time":172000,"text":"you're likely to go the wrong side of that dividing line."},{"time":175000,"text":"We had -- we were being attacked by British Airways."},{"time":182000,"text":"They were trying to put our airline out of business,"},{"time":185000,"text":"and they launched what's become known as the dirty tricks campaign."},{"time":190000,"text":"And I realized that the whole empire was likely to come crashing down"},{"time":195000,"text":"unless I chipped in a chip."},{"time":197000,"text":"And in order to protect the jobs of the people who worked for the airline,"},{"time":201000,"text":"and protect the jobs of the people who worked for the record company,"},{"time":205000,"text":"I had to sell the family jewelry to protect the airline."}]},{"cues":[{"time":211000,"text":"CA: Post-Napster, you're looking like a bit of a genius, actually,"},{"time":214000,"text":"for that as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215000,"text":"RB: Yeah, as it turned out, it proved to be the right move."},{"time":221000,"text":"But, yeah, it was sad at the time, but we moved on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":227000,"text":"CA: Now, you use the Virgin brand a lot"},{"time":229000,"text":"and it seems like you're getting synergy from one thing to the other."},{"time":232000,"text":"What does the brand stand for in your head?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":235000,"text":"RB: Well, I like to think it stands for quality,"},{"time":237000,"text":"that you know, if somebody comes across a Virgin company, they --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":241000,"text":"CA: They are quality, Richard. Come on now, everyone says quality. Spirit?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":243000,"text":"RB: No, but I was going to move on this."},{"time":245000,"text":"We have a lot of fun and I think the people who work for it enjoy it."},{"time":251000,"text":"As I say, we go in and shake up other industries,"},{"time":254000,"text":"and I think, you know, we do it differently"},{"time":258000,"text":"and I think that industries are not quite the same"},{"time":260000,"text":"as a result of Virgin attacking the market."}]},{"cues":[{"time":262000,"text":"CA: I mean, there are a few launches you've done"},{"time":265000,"text":"where the brand maybe hasn't worked quite as well."},{"time":267000,"text":"I mean, Virgin Brides -- what happened there?"},{"time":270000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":272000,"text":"RB: We couldn't find any customers."},{"time":274000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":277000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":278000,"text":"CA: I was actually also curious why --"},{"time":280000,"text":"I think you missed an opportunity with your condoms launch. You called it Mates."},{"time":283000,"text":"I mean, couldn't you have used the Virgin brand for that as well?"},{"time":287000,"text":"Ain't virgin no longer, or something."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290000,"text":"RB: Again, we may have had problems finding customers."},{"time":292000,"text":"I mean, we had -- often, when you launch a company and you get customer complaints,"},{"time":298000,"text":"you know, you can deal with them."},{"time":300000,"text":"But about three months after the launch of the condom company,"},{"time":302000,"text":"I had a letter, a complaint,"},{"time":305000,"text":"and I sat down and wrote a long letter back to this lady apologizing profusely."},{"time":309000,"text":"But obviously, there wasn't a lot I could do about it."},{"time":312000,"text":"And then six months later, or nine months after the problem had taken,"},{"time":318000,"text":"I got this delightful letter with a picture of the baby"},{"time":321000,"text":"asking if I'd be godfather, which I became."},{"time":326000,"text":"So, it all worked out well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":328000,"text":"CA: Really? You should have brought a picture. That's wonderful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":331000,"text":"RB: I should have."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332000,"text":"CA: So, just help us with some of the numbers."},{"time":334000,"text":"I mean, what are the numbers on this?"},{"time":336000,"text":"I mean, how big is the group overall?"},{"time":338000,"text":"How much -- what's the total revenue?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":340000,"text":"RB: It's about 25 billion dollars now, in total."}]},{"cues":[{"time":343000,"text":"CA: And how many employees?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":344000,"text":"RB: About 55,000."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347000,"text":"CA: So, you've been photographed in various ways at various times"},{"time":351000,"text":"and never worrying about putting your dignity on the line or anything like that."},{"time":359000,"text":"What was that? Was that real?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":363000,"text":"RB: Yeah. We were launching a megastore in Los Angeles, I think."},{"time":366000,"text":"No, I mean, I think --"},{"time":367000,"text":"CA: But is that your hair?"},{"time":368000,"text":"RB: No."},{"time":372000,"text":"CA: What was that one?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":374000,"text":"RB: Dropping in for tea."}]},{"cues":[{"time":375000,"text":"CA: OK."},{"time":376000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":379000,"text":"RB: Ah, that was quite fun. That was a wonderful car-boat in which --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":382000,"text":"CA: Oh, that car that we -- actually we --"},{"time":384000,"text":"it was a TEDster event there, I think."},{"time":387000,"text":"Is that -- could you still pause on that one actually, for a minute?"},{"time":389000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":390000,"text":"RB: It's a tough job, isn't it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":391000,"text":"CA: I mean, it is a tough job."},{"time":393000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":394000,"text":"When I first came to America, I used to try this with employees as well"},{"time":398000,"text":"and they kind of -- they have these different rules over here,"},{"time":400000,"text":"it's very strange."}]},{"cues":[{"time":401000,"text":"RB: I know, I have -- the lawyers say you mustn't do things like that, but --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":406000,"text":"CA: I mean, speaking of which, tell us about --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":407000,"text":"RB: \"Pammy\" we launched, you know --"},{"time":409000,"text":"mistakenly thought we could take on Coca-Cola,"},{"time":411000,"text":"and we launched a cola bottle called \"The Pammy\""},{"time":416000,"text":"and it was shaped a bit like Pamela Anderson."},{"time":419000,"text":"But the trouble is, it kept on tipping over, but --"},{"time":422000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":425000,"text":"CA: Designed by Philippe Starck perhaps?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":427000,"text":"RB: Of course."}]},{"cues":[{"time":429000,"text":"CA: So, we'll just run a couple more pictures here. Virgin Brides. Very nice."},{"time":434000,"text":"And, OK, so stop there. This was -- you had some award I think?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":441000,"text":"RB: Yeah, well, 25 years earlier, we'd launched the Sex Pistols'"},{"time":446000,"text":"\"God Save The Queen,\" and I'd certainly never expected"},{"time":449000,"text":"that 25 years later -- that she'd actually knight us."},{"time":452000,"text":"But somehow, she must have had a forgetful memory, I think."}]},{"cues":[{"time":456000,"text":"CA: Well, God saved her and you got your just reward."},{"time":459000,"text":"Do you like to be called Sir Richard, or how?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":462000,"text":"RB: Nobody's ever called me Sir Richard."},{"time":464000,"text":"Occasionally in America, I hear people saying Sir Richard"},{"time":467000,"text":"and think there's some Shakespearean play taking place."},{"time":471000,"text":"But nowhere else anyway."}]},{"cues":[{"time":475000,"text":"CA: OK. So can you use your knighthood for anything or is it just ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":480000,"text":"RB: No. I suppose if you're having problems"},{"time":484000,"text":"getting a booking in a restaurant or something,"},{"time":486000,"text":"that might be worth using it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":487000,"text":"CA: You know, it's not Richard Branson. It's Sir Richard Branson."}]},{"cues":[{"time":492000,"text":"RB: I'll go get the secretary to use it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495000,"text":"CA: OK. So let's look at the space thing."},{"time":498000,"text":"I think, with us, we've got a video that shows what you're up to,"},{"time":502000,"text":"and Virgin Galactic up in the air. (Video)"},{"time":509000,"text":"So that's the Bert Rutan designed spaceship?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":512000,"text":"RB: Yeah, it'll be ready in -- well, ready in 12 months"},{"time":517000,"text":"and then we do 12 months extensive testing."},{"time":520000,"text":"And then 24 months from now,"},{"time":522000,"text":"people will be able to take a ride into space."}]},{"cues":[{"time":529000,"text":"CA: So this interior is Philippe Starcke designed?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":532000,"text":"RB: Philippe has done the -- yeah, quite a bit of it:"},{"time":537000,"text":"the logos and he's building the space station in New Mexico."},{"time":542000,"text":"And basically, he's just taken an eye"},{"time":545000,"text":"and the space station will be one giant eye,"},{"time":550000,"text":"so when you're in space,"},{"time":552000,"text":"you ought to be able to see this massive eye looking up at you."},{"time":555000,"text":"And when you land, you'll be able to go back into this giant eye."},{"time":561000,"text":"But he's an absolute genius when it comes to design."}]},{"cues":[{"time":565000,"text":"CA: But you didn't have him design the engine?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":568000,"text":"RB: Philippe is quite erratic,"},{"time":570000,"text":"so I think that he wouldn't be the best person to design the engine, no."}]},{"cues":[{"time":574000,"text":"CA: He gave a wonderful talk here two days ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":576000,"text":"RB: Yeah? No, he is a --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":577000,"text":"CA: Well, some people found it wonderful,"},{"time":579000,"text":"some people found it completely bizarre."},{"time":581000,"text":"But, I personally found it wonderful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":583000,"text":"RB: He's a wonderful enthusiast, which is why I love him. But ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":589000,"text":"CA: So, now, you've always had this exploration bug in you."},{"time":595000,"text":"Have you ever regretted that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":597000,"text":"RB: Many times."},{"time":598000,"text":"I mean, I think with the ballooning and boating expeditions we've done in the past."},{"time":605000,"text":"Well, I got pulled out of the sea I think six times by helicopters, so --"},{"time":609000,"text":"and each time, I didn't expect to come home to tell the tale."},{"time":613000,"text":"So in those moments,"},{"time":615000,"text":"you certainly wonder what you're doing up there or --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":618000,"text":"CA: What was the closest you got to --"},{"time":620000,"text":"when did you think, this is it, I might be on my way out?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":624000,"text":"RB: Well, I think the balloon adventures were -- each one was,"},{"time":629000,"text":"each one, actually, I think we came close."},{"time":632000,"text":"And, I mean, first of all we --"},{"time":635000,"text":"nobody had actually crossed the Atlantic in a hot air balloon before,"},{"time":639000,"text":"so we had to build a hot air balloon that was capable of flying in the jet stream,"},{"time":646000,"text":"and we weren't quite sure,"},{"time":648000,"text":"when a balloon actually got into the jet stream,"},{"time":650000,"text":"whether it would actually survive the 200, 220 miles an hour winds that you can find up there."},{"time":656000,"text":"And so, just the initial lift off from Sugarloaf to cross the Atlantic,"},{"time":662000,"text":"as we were pushing into the jet stream, this enormous balloon --"},{"time":665000,"text":"the top of the balloon ended up going at a couple of hundred miles an hour,"},{"time":670000,"text":"the capsule that we were in at the bottom was going at maybe two miles an hour,"},{"time":674000,"text":"and it just took off."},{"time":676000,"text":"And it was like holding onto a thousand horses."},{"time":680000,"text":"And we were just crossing every finger,"},{"time":683000,"text":"praying that the balloon would hold together, which, fortunately, it did."},{"time":689000,"text":"But the ends of all those balloon trips were, you know --"},{"time":694000,"text":"something seemed to go wrong every time,"},{"time":696000,"text":"and on that particular occasion, the more experienced balloonist who was with me"},{"time":702000,"text":"jumped, and left me holding on for dear life."},{"time":707000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":710000,"text":"CA: Did he tell you to jump, or he just said, \"I'm out of here!\" and ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":713000,"text":"RB: No, he told me jump, but once his weight had gone,"},{"time":717000,"text":"the balloon just shot up to 12,000 feet and I ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":723000,"text":"CA: And you inspired an Ian McEwan novel I think with that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":726000,"text":"RB: Yeah. No, I put on my oxygen mask and stood on top of the balloon,"},{"time":730000,"text":"with my parachute, looking at the swirling clouds below,"},{"time":733000,"text":"trying to pluck up my courage to jump into the North Sea, which --"},{"time":738000,"text":"and it was a very, very, very lonely few moments."},{"time":740000,"text":"But, anyway, we managed to survive it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":742000,"text":"CA: Did you jump? Or it came down in the end?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":744000,"text":"RB: Well, I knew I had about half an hour's fuel left,"},{"time":750000,"text":"and I also knew that the chances were that if I jumped,"},{"time":754000,"text":"I would only have a couple of minutes of life left."},{"time":757000,"text":"So I climbed back into the capsule and just desperately tried"},{"time":761000,"text":"to make sure that I was making the right decision."},{"time":764000,"text":"And wrote some notes to my family. And then climbed back up again,"},{"time":768000,"text":"looked down at those clouds again,"},{"time":769000,"text":"climbed back into the capsule again."},{"time":771000,"text":"And then finally, just thought, there's a better way."},{"time":774000,"text":"I've got, you know, this enormous balloon above me,"},{"time":777000,"text":"it's the biggest parachute ever, why not use it?"},{"time":782000,"text":"And so I managed to fly the balloon down through the clouds,"},{"time":787000,"text":"and about 50 feet, before I hit the sea, threw myself over."},{"time":791000,"text":"And the balloon hit the sea"},{"time":793000,"text":"and went shooting back up to 10,000 feet without me."},{"time":797000,"text":"But it was a wonderful feeling being in that water and --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":800000,"text":"CA: What did you write to your family?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":803000,"text":"RB: Just what you would do in a situation like that:"},{"time":807000,"text":"just I love you very much. And"},{"time":810000,"text":"I'd already written them a letter before going on this trip, which --"},{"time":815000,"text":"just in case anything had happened."},{"time":817000,"text":"But fortunately, they never had to use it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":822000,"text":"CA: Your companies have had incredible PR value out of these heroics."},{"time":829000,"text":"The years -- and until I stopped looking at the polls,"},{"time":834000,"text":"you were sort of regarded as this great hero in the U.K. and elsewhere."},{"time":838000,"text":"And cynics might say, you know, this is just a smart business guy"},{"time":842000,"text":"doing what it takes to execute his particular style of marketing."},{"time":847000,"text":"How much was the PR value part of this?"},{"time":852000,"text":"RB: Well, of course, the PR experts said that as an airline owner,"},{"time":859000,"text":"the last thing you should be doing is heading off in balloons and boats,"},{"time":864000,"text":"and crashing into the seas."},{"time":867000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":871000,"text":"CA: They have a point, Richard."}]},{"cues":[{"time":873000,"text":"RB: In fact, I think our airline took a full page ad at the time saying,"},{"time":877000,"text":"you know, come on, Richard,"},{"time":879000,"text":"there are better ways of crossing the Atlantic."},{"time":882000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":883000,"text":"CA: To do all this,"},{"time":885000,"text":"you must have been a genius from the get-go, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":889000,"text":"RB: Well, I won't contradict that."},{"time":892000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":893000,"text":"CA: OK, this isn't exactly hardball. OK."}]},{"cues":[{"time":897000,"text":"Didn't -- weren't you just terrible at school?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":901000,"text":"RB: I was dyslexic. I had no understanding of schoolwork whatsoever."},{"time":912000,"text":"I certainly would have failed IQ tests."},{"time":915000,"text":"And it was one of the reasons I left school when I was 15 years old."},{"time":922000,"text":"And if I -- if I'm not interested in something, I don't grasp it."},{"time":930000,"text":"As somebody who's dyslexic,"},{"time":931000,"text":"you also have some quite bizarre situations."},{"time":933000,"text":"I mean, for instance, I've had to -- you know,"},{"time":938000,"text":"I've been running the largest group of private companies in Europe,"},{"time":941000,"text":"but haven't been able to know the difference between net and gross."},{"time":947000,"text":"And so the board meetings have been fascinating."},{"time":950000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":951000,"text":"And so, it's like, good news or bad news?"},{"time":953000,"text":"And generally, the people would say, oh, well that's bad news."}]},{"cues":[{"time":956000,"text":"CA: But just to clarify, the 25 billion dollars is gross, right? That's gross?"},{"time":959000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":960000,"text":"RB: Well, I hope it's net actually, having --"},{"time":963000,"text":"(Laughter) --"},{"time":966000,"text":"I've got it right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":968000,"text":"CA: No, trust me, it's gross."},{"time":970000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":973000,"text":"RB: So, when I turned 50, somebody took me outside the boardroom and said,"},{"time":977000,"text":"\"Look Richard, here's a -- let me draw on a diagram."},{"time":980000,"text":"Here's a net in the sea,"},{"time":982000,"text":"and the fish have been pulled from the sea into this net."},{"time":986000,"text":"And that's the profits you've got left over in this little net,"},{"time":989000,"text":"everything else is eaten.\""},{"time":991000,"text":"And I finally worked it all out."},{"time":994000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":995000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":997000,"text":"CA: But, I mean, at school -- so as well as being,"},{"time":1000000,"text":"you know, doing pretty miserably academically,"},{"time":1002000,"text":"but you were also the captain of the cricket and football teams."},{"time":1005000,"text":"So you were kind of a -- you were a natural leader,"},{"time":1007000,"text":"but just a bit of a ... Were you a rebel then, or how would you ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1013000,"text":"RB: Yeah, I think I was a bit of a maverick and -- but I ... And I was,"},{"time":1021000,"text":"yeah, I was fortunately good at sport,"},{"time":1023000,"text":"and so at least I had something to excel at, at school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1028000,"text":"CA: And some bizarre things happened just earlier in your life."},{"time":1030000,"text":"I mean, there's the story about your mother"},{"time":1032000,"text":"allegedly dumping you in a field, aged four, and saying \"OK, walk home.\""},{"time":1037000,"text":"Did this really happen?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1038000,"text":"RB: She was, you know,"},{"time":1040000,"text":"she felt that we needed to stand on our own two feet from an early age."},{"time":1043000,"text":"So she did things to us, which now she'd be arrested for,"},{"time":1047000,"text":"such as pushing us out of the car,"},{"time":1051000,"text":"and telling us to find our own way to Granny's,"},{"time":1053000,"text":"about five miles before we actually got there."},{"time":1057000,"text":"And making us go on wonderful, long bike rides."},{"time":1060000,"text":"And we were never allowed to watch television and the like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1063000,"text":"CA: But is there a risk here?"},{"time":1064000,"text":"I mean, there's a lot of people in the room who are wealthy, and they've got kids,"},{"time":1067000,"text":"and we've got this dilemma about how you bring them up."},{"time":1070000,"text":"Do you look at the current generation of kids coming up and think"},{"time":1073000,"text":"they're too coddled, they don't know what they've got,"},{"time":1075000,"text":"we're going to raise a generation of privileged ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1077000,"text":"RB: No, I think if you're bringing up kids,"},{"time":1080000,"text":"you just want to smother them with love and praise and enthusiasm."},{"time":1087000,"text":"So I don't think you can mollycoddle your kids too much really."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1093000,"text":"CA: You didn't turn out too bad, I have to say, I'm ..."},{"time":1096000,"text":"Your headmaster said to you --"},{"time":1098000,"text":"I mean he found you kind of an enigma at your school --"},{"time":1101000,"text":"he said, you're either going to be a millionaire or go to prison,"},{"time":1104000,"text":"and I'm not sure which."},{"time":1106000,"text":"Which of those happened first?"},{"time":1109000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1110000,"text":"RB: Well, I've done both. I think I went to prison first."},{"time":1114000,"text":"I was actually prosecuted under two quite ancient acts in the U.K."},{"time":1120000,"text":"I was prosecuted under the 1889 Venereal Diseases Act"},{"time":1124000,"text":"and the 1916 Indecent Advertisements Act."},{"time":1126000,"text":"On the first occasion, for mentioning the word venereal disease in public, which --"},{"time":1132000,"text":"we had a center where we would help young people who had problems."},{"time":1136000,"text":"And one of the problems young people have is venereal disease."},{"time":1139000,"text":"And there's an ancient law that says"},{"time":1140000,"text":"you can't actually mention the word venereal disease or print it in public."},{"time":1144000,"text":"So the police knocked on the door, and told us they were going to arrest us"},{"time":1147000,"text":"if we carried on mentioning the word venereal disease."},{"time":1149000,"text":"We changed it to social diseases"},{"time":1151000,"text":"and people came along with acne and spots,"},{"time":1153000,"text":"but nobody came with VD any more."},{"time":1155000,"text":"So, we put it back to VD and promptly got arrested."},{"time":1159000,"text":"And then subsequently, \"Never Mind the Bollocks, Here's the Sex Pistols,\""},{"time":1163000,"text":"the word bollocks, the police decided was a rude word and so we were arrested"},{"time":1170000,"text":"for using the word bollocks on the Sex Pistols' album."},{"time":1173000,"text":"And John Mortimer, the playwright, defended us."},{"time":1177000,"text":"And he asked if I could find a linguistics expert"},{"time":1182000,"text":"to come up with a different definition of the word bollocks."},{"time":1186000,"text":"And so I rang up Nottingham University,"},{"time":1188000,"text":"and I asked to talk to the professor of linguistics."},{"time":1190000,"text":"And he said, \"Look, bollocks is not a -- has nothing to do with balls whatsoever."},{"time":1195000,"text":"It's actually a nickname given to priests in the eighteenth century.\""},{"time":1199000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1202000,"text":"And he went, \"Furthermore, I'm a priest myself.\""},{"time":1206000,"text":"And so I said, \"Would you mind coming to the court?\""},{"time":1208000,"text":"And he said he'd be delighted. And I said --"},{"time":1210000,"text":"and he said, \"Would you like me to wear my dog collar?\""},{"time":1212000,"text":"And I said, \"Yes, definitely. Please.\""},{"time":1214000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1216000,"text":"CA: That's great."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1217000,"text":"RB: So our key witness argued that it was actually"},{"time":1219000,"text":"\"Never Mind the Priest, Here's the Sex Pistols.\""},{"time":1221000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1223000,"text":"And the judge found us -- reluctantly found us not guilty, so ..."},{"time":1226000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1227000,"text":"CA: That is outrageous."},{"time":1230000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":1232000,"text":"So seriously, is there a dark side?"},{"time":1237000,"text":"A lot of people would say there's no way"},{"time":1239000,"text":"that someone could put together this incredible collection of businesses"},{"time":1242000,"text":"without knifing a few people in the back,"},{"time":1245000,"text":"you know, doing some ugly things."},{"time":1247000,"text":"You've been accused of being ruthless."},{"time":1249000,"text":"There was a nasty biography written about you by someone."},{"time":1251000,"text":"Is any of it true? Is there an element of truth in it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1255000,"text":"RB: I don't actually think that the stereotype"},{"time":1258000,"text":"of a businessperson treading all over people to get to the top,"},{"time":1263000,"text":"generally speaking, works."},{"time":1265000,"text":"I think if you treat people well,"},{"time":1267000,"text":"people will come back and come back for more."},{"time":1272000,"text":"And I think all you have in life is your reputation"},{"time":1275000,"text":"and it's a very small world."},{"time":1280000,"text":"And I actually think that the best way"},{"time":1284000,"text":"of becoming a successful business leader is dealing with people fairly and well,"},{"time":1291000,"text":"and I like to think that's how we run Virgin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1296000,"text":"CA: And what about the people who love you and who see you spending --"},{"time":1300000,"text":"you keep getting caught up in these new projects,"},{"time":1302000,"text":"but it almost feels like you're addicted to launching new stuff."},{"time":1305000,"text":"You get excited by an idea and, kapow!"},{"time":1307000,"text":"I mean, do you think about life balance?"},{"time":1310000,"text":"How do your family feel about"},{"time":1312000,"text":"each time you step into something big and new?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1315000,"text":"RB: I also believe that being a father's incredibly important,"},{"time":1319000,"text":"so from the time the kids were very young,"},{"time":1322000,"text":"you know, when they go on holiday, I go on holiday with them."},{"time":1326000,"text":"And so we spend a very good sort of three months away together."},{"time":1332000,"text":"Yes, I'll, you know, be in touch. We're very lucky,"},{"time":1335000,"text":"we have this tiny little island in the Caribbean and we can --"},{"time":1339000,"text":"so I can take them there and we can bring friends,"},{"time":1343000,"text":"and we can play together,"},{"time":1345000,"text":"but I can also keep in touch with what's going on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1349000,"text":"CA: You started talking in recent years"},{"time":1351000,"text":"about this term capitalist philanthropy."},{"time":1353000,"text":"What is that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1355000,"text":"RB: Capitalism has been proven to be a system that works."},{"time":1359000,"text":"You know, the alternative, communism, has not worked."},{"time":1364000,"text":"But the problem with capitalism is"},{"time":1366000,"text":"extreme wealth ends up in the hands of a few people,"},{"time":1369000,"text":"and therefore extreme responsibility, I think, goes with that wealth."},{"time":1374000,"text":"And I think it's important that the individuals,"},{"time":1378000,"text":"who are in that fortunate position, do not end up competing"},{"time":1383000,"text":"for bigger and bigger boats, and bigger and bigger cars,"},{"time":1385000,"text":"but, you know, use that money to either create new jobs"},{"time":1391000,"text":"or to tackle issues around the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1395000,"text":"CA: And what are the issues that you worry about most, care most about,"},{"time":1398000,"text":"want to turn your resources toward?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1402000,"text":"RB: Well, there's -- I mean there's a lot of issues."},{"time":1405000,"text":"I mean global warming certainly is a massive threat to mankind"},{"time":1412000,"text":"and we are putting a lot of time and energy into,"},{"time":1416000,"text":"A, trying to come up with alternative fuels"},{"time":1420000,"text":"and, B, you know, we just launched this prize, which is really a prize"},{"time":1429000,"text":"in case we don't get an answer on alternative fuels,"},{"time":1433000,"text":"in case we don't actually manage to get the carbon emissions"},{"time":1436000,"text":"cut down quickly, and in case we go through the tipping point."},{"time":1439000,"text":"We need to try to encourage people to come up with a way"},{"time":1443000,"text":"of extracting carbon out of the Earth's atmosphere."},{"time":1446000,"text":"And we just -- you know, there weren't really people"},{"time":1449000,"text":"working on that before, so we wanted people to try to --"},{"time":1453000,"text":"all the best brains in the world to start thinking about that,"},{"time":1456000,"text":"and also to try to extract the methane"},{"time":1458000,"text":"out of the Earth's atmosphere as well."},{"time":1461000,"text":"And actually, we've had about 15,000 people fill in the forms"},{"time":1466000,"text":"saying they want to give it a go."},{"time":1468000,"text":"And so we only need one, so we're hopeful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1471000,"text":"CA: And you're also working in Africa on a couple of projects?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1475000,"text":"RB: Yes, I mean, we've got -- we're setting up something called"},{"time":1479000,"text":"the war room, which is maybe the wrong word."},{"time":1481000,"text":"We're trying to -- maybe we'll change it -- but anyway, it's a war room"},{"time":1485000,"text":"to try to coordinate all the attack that's going on in Africa,"},{"time":1489000,"text":"all the different social problems in Africa,"},{"time":1492000,"text":"and try to look at best practices."},{"time":1496000,"text":"So, for instance,"},{"time":1499000,"text":"there's a doctor in Africa that's found that"},{"time":1502000,"text":"if you give a mother antiretroviral drugs at 24 weeks, when she's pregnant,"},{"time":1508000,"text":"that the baby will not have HIV when it's born."},{"time":1515000,"text":"And so disseminating that information to"},{"time":1520000,"text":"around the rest of Africa is important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1522000,"text":"CA: The war room sounds, it sounds powerful and dramatic."},{"time":1525000,"text":"And is there a risk that the kind of the business heroes of the West"},{"time":1530000,"text":"get so excited about -- I mean, they're used to having an idea,"},{"time":1534000,"text":"getting stuff done, and they believe profoundly"},{"time":1537000,"text":"in their ability to make a difference in the world."},{"time":1539000,"text":"Is there a risk that we go to places like Africa and say,"},{"time":1542000,"text":"we've got to fix this problem and we can do it,"},{"time":1545000,"text":"I've got all these billions of dollars, you know, da, da, da --"},{"time":1548000,"text":"here's the big idea. And kind of take a much more complex situation"},{"time":1552000,"text":"and actually end up making a mess of it. Do you worry about that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1557000,"text":"RB: Well, first of all, on this particular situation, we're actually --"},{"time":1564000,"text":"we're working with the government on it."},{"time":1566000,"text":"I mean, Thabo Mbeki's had his problems with accepting"},{"time":1570000,"text":"HIV and AIDS are related, but this is a way, I think,"},{"time":1575000,"text":"of him tackling this problem and instead of the world criticizing him,"},{"time":1581000,"text":"it's a way of working with him, with his government."},{"time":1584000,"text":"It's important that if people do go to Africa and do try to help,"},{"time":1586000,"text":"they don't just go in there and then leave after a few years."},{"time":1589000,"text":"It's got to be consistent."},{"time":1591000,"text":"But I think business leaders can bring their entrepreneurial know-how"},{"time":1597000,"text":"and help governments approach things slightly differently."},{"time":1601000,"text":"For instance, we're setting up clinics in Africa"},{"time":1604000,"text":"where we're going to be giving"},{"time":1606000,"text":"free antiretroviral drugs, free TB treatment"},{"time":1608000,"text":"and free malaria treatment."},{"time":1611000,"text":"But we're also trying to make them self-sustaining clinics,"},{"time":1614000,"text":"so that people pay for some other aspects."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1618000,"text":"CA: I mean a lot of cynics say about someone like yourself, or Bill Gates,"},{"time":1622000,"text":"or whatever, that this is really being -- it's almost driven by"},{"time":1625000,"text":"some sort of desire again, you know, for the right image,"},{"time":1628000,"text":"for guilt avoidance and not like a real philanthropic instinct."},{"time":1633000,"text":"What would you say to them?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1634000,"text":"RB: Well, I think that everybody --"},{"time":1636000,"text":"people do things for a whole variety of different reasons"},{"time":1640000,"text":"and I think that, you know, when I'm on me deathbed,"},{"time":1642000,"text":"I will want to feel that I've made a difference"},{"time":1645000,"text":"to other people's lives."},{"time":1647000,"text":"And that may be a selfish thing to think,"},{"time":1650000,"text":"but it's the way I've been brought up."},{"time":1652000,"text":"I think if I'm in a position to"},{"time":1654000,"text":"radically change other people's lives for the better,"},{"time":1657000,"text":"I should do so."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1659000,"text":"CA: How old are you?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1660000,"text":"RB: I'm 56."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1661000,"text":"CA: I mean, the psychologist Erik Erikson says that -- as I understand him"},{"time":1666000,"text":"and I'm a total amateur -- but that during 30s, 40s people are driven by"},{"time":1672000,"text":"this desire to grow and that's where they get their fulfillment."},{"time":1677000,"text":"50s, 60s, the mode of operation shifts more to the quest for wisdom"},{"time":1681000,"text":"and a search for legacy."},{"time":1683000,"text":"I mean, it seems like you're still"},{"time":1685000,"text":"a little bit in the growth phases,"},{"time":1687000,"text":"you're still doing these incredible new plans."},{"time":1689000,"text":"How much do you think about legacy,"},{"time":1691000,"text":"and what would you like your legacy to be?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1696000,"text":"RB: I don't think I think too much about legacy."},{"time":1699000,"text":"I mean, I like to -- you know, my grandmother lived to 101,"},{"time":1705000,"text":"so hopefully I've got another 30 or 40 years to go."},{"time":1709000,"text":"No, I just want to live life to its full."},{"time":1715000,"text":"You know, if I can make a difference,"},{"time":1717000,"text":"I hope to be able to make a difference."},{"time":1719000,"text":"And I think one of the positive things at the moment is"},{"time":1722000,"text":"you've got Sergey and Larry from Google, for instance,"},{"time":1726000,"text":"who are good friends."},{"time":1728000,"text":"And, thank God, you've got two people"},{"time":1731000,"text":"who genuinely care about the world and with that kind of wealth."},{"time":1735000,"text":"If they had that kind of wealth and they didn't care about the world,"},{"time":1738000,"text":"it would be very worrying."},{"time":1740000,"text":"And you know they're going to make a hell of a difference to the world."},{"time":1743000,"text":"And I think it's important"},{"time":1745000,"text":"that people in that kind of position do make a difference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1749000,"text":"CA: Well, Richard, when I was starting off in business,"},{"time":1750000,"text":"I knew nothing about it and I also was sort of --"},{"time":1753000,"text":"I thought that business people were supposed to just be ruthless"},{"time":1755000,"text":"and that that was the only way you could have a chance of succeeding."},{"time":1759000,"text":"And you actually did inspire me. I looked at you, I thought,"},{"time":1761000,"text":"well, he's made it. Maybe there is a different way."},{"time":1763000,"text":"So I would like to thank you for that inspiration,"},{"time":1766000,"text":"and for coming to TED today. Thank you."},{"time":1768000,"text":"Thank you so much."},{"time":1769000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}